Upgrading from v0.4 or earlier to v0.5
======================================

Because of the changes in v0.5 with respect to the configuration files the 
following approach can be taken:

. cp path_to_gitstat/config.php path_to_gitstat/gstat_rw/config/dbconfig.php
. cp path_to_gitstat/config.php path_to_gitstat/gstat_rw/config/gitstatconfig.php

The new configuration parameters can be checked by logging in as an adminstrator
and visiting the admin page.

path_to_gitstat/config.php  can be removed as it's no longer used.
